---
title: Smoked Cheddar Burgers with Garlic and Rosemary Foil-Pouch Potatoes
description: Grab the cooler and get ready to hit the grill! Delight your tastebuds with this smoked cheddar and fig-topped rosemary burger. An elegant side of garlic grilled potatoes rounds out this long weekend winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smoked-cheddar-burgers-91327677.jpg
